<h3 id="designs">Designs</h3>

<p>I had all the variations of the colour combinations, but selected what I felt the best combinations were based on the contrast. I also had an issue with merging paths on Inkscape, resulting in varying line thickness and a pointed edge on the banner and heart intersection. It was later removed for the design that was made into a badge, however it can be seen in these images.</p>

