<h3 id="bonus-designs">Bonus Designs</h3>

<p>I didnâ€™t know how to use Inkscape when I first designed it, so the lines were drawn freehand or by using the line option in Photoshop. I was also experimenting with colour combinations at the time, so I used the paint bucket on the freehand lines, which resulted in an incredibly pixelated image (if you zoom in).</p>

